 3 given by\nRabinovitch to provide a structural description of the semiorders of dimension\nat most 2. From this description, we are able to determine the ordinary\ngenerating for the semiorders of dimension at most 2.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jan 2018 19:58:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jul 2018 14:00:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2020 14:58:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-20"}
